Class LongList<T>

Namespace
Cobilas.Collections.Generic
Assembly
Cobilas.Core.dll

Represents a long, strongly typed list of objects that can be accessed by index. Provides methods for searching, sorting, and manipulating lists.

[Serializable]
public class LongList<T> : ILongList<T>, ILongCollection<T>, IReadOnlyLongList<T>, IReadOnlyLongCollection<T>, IEnumerable<T>, ILongList, ILongCollection, IEnumerable, ICloneable
